      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like that's just a \"both sides\" answer. like you're not really saying anything. if you look at how it's actually happening in schools or workplaces, isn't it mostly just people getting silenced for having different views? it seems pretty much pretty clear that it's becoming a censorship thing.",
